string.text: Dziakujučy zołatu i srebru, jakija zdabyvajecca va ŭzhorkach i skałach, žychary hetaha kraju zjaŭlajucca samymi bahatymi na Zachadasie.
Ludzi Poŭnačy - ciahavitaja paroda. Naščadki Pieršych Ludziej, jakimi kiravali Karali Poŭnačy da zavajovy Aehona.
Dotrakijcy - vajaŭničy kačavy narod, što pierasoŭvajecca vialikimi ordami pa łuhach Uschodasa. Ordy zvyčajna zavucca chałasarami.
Žaleznanarodžanyja nasialajuć Žaleznyja Vyspy i pakłaniajucca Patanułamu Bohu. Dla ich rabavańnie zachodnich bierahoŭ Zachadasa - ład žyćcia.

Darnijcy ŭ bolšaści svajoj zjaŭlajucca naščadkami naroda, jaki ŭźnik kala Raki Rojn na Uschodasie. Pryncesa Nimieryja źbiehła sa svajoj radzimy, ratujučysia ad Valiryjcaŭ, i pasialiłasia ŭ Dornie z vialikaj kolkaściu haściej. Toje tłumačyć, čamu bolšaść Darnijcaŭ vyhladajuć inačaj za zvyčajnych Zachadasaŭ.
Najbahaciejšy z Volnych Haradoŭ. Tut znachodzicca Žalezny Bank i Dom Čornaha i Biełaha.
Naščadki Pieršych Ludziej, jakija patrapili ŭ pastku na poŭnačy ad ściany 8000 hadoŭ tamu. Narody, što žyvuć na poŭdnie ad ściany, časta zavuć ich adzičełymi.

Vajskovy orden, jakomu daručana baranić karaleŭstvy ludziej ad usiakaj pahrozy z poŭnačy ad ściany. U ich šerahach časta sustrakajucca badziahi i złačyncy, jakija sprabujuć paźbiehnuć lutaha hnievu pravasudździa.
Damy, jakija paklalisia ŭ viernaści łordam svajho kraju, ale nasamreč addanyja tolki sabie.
Pieršyja Andały, jakija prybyli ŭ Zachadas, pasialilisia ŭ miascovaści, viadomaj siońnia jak Dalina. Heta surovy łandšaft, atočany Harami Miesiaca.

Žychary hetaha kraju žyvuć na skryžavańni šlachoŭ niekalkich inšych mahutnych karaleŭstvaŭ. U časy zavajovy Tarharyjenaŭ račnyja ziemli znachodzilisia pad uładaj Žaleznanarodžanych. Paŭstańnie pad pravadyrstvam Doma Talli dapamahło Aehonu zavajavać hety kraj. U vyniku, u hetym krai byli atrymany vielizarnyja vaładarstvy.
Žychary vyspaŭ i žychary kala Zatoki Čornaja Vada paśla paŭstańnia Robierta pierajšli pad kantrol Stańnisa Barateona.

Žychary hetych ziemlaŭ nazvany tak z-za častych dzikich štormaŭ, jakija abrušvajucca na ichniaje ŭschodniaje ŭźbiarežža z boku Vuzkaha Mora. Da zavajovy Aehonam hety kraj składaŭ ułasnaje suvierennaje karaleŭstva, jakoje mieła nazvu Štarmavoje Karaleŭstva.
Tutejšyja žychary zjaŭlajucca vychadcami druhoha haspadarstva pa vieličyni z Siami Karaleŭstvaŭ, paśla Paŭnočnaha. Hety kraj maje samyja ŭradlivyja ziemli ŭva ŭsim Zachadasie.

Hetyja ludzi - naščadki staroj Staroj Impieryi His, jakaja była źniščana Valiryjcami padčas Hiskarskich Vojnaŭ. U haradach Zatoki Zaniavolnikaŭ dahetul praktykujecca šmat starych Hiskarskich zvyčajaŭ.
Žychary sprečnych ziemlaŭ pamiž Račnymi i Štarmavymi Ziemlami, jakija z časoŭ Aehona Zavajoŭnika kirujucca niepasredna karalom z Karaleŭskaj Prystani.
Volny horad Norvas - sapraŭdnaja teakratyja, jakoj kirujuć Baradatyja Śviatary. Štodzionnaje žyćcio ludziej stroha padnačalvajecca trom zvanam.
Naščadki tych, chto pakinuŭ Valiryju da źniščeńnia hetaha horada kataklizmam.
Žychary pieršaha Volnaha Horada Uschodasa, jakoj zasnavali Valiryjcy.
Žychary adnaho z Volnych Haradoŭ Uschodasa. Viadomaha jak Horad Viedźmaroŭ.
Žychary samaha paŭnočnaha z Volnych Haradoŭ, źmiescavanaha na vyśpie ŭ Dryhučym Mory.
Žychary samaha zachodniaha z Volnych Haradoŭ, źmiescavanaha na bierazie Zatoki Pentos.
Žychary samaha raźvitaha z Volnych Haradoŭ, źmiescavanaha na bierazie Mora Mirt.
Ludzi z Volnaha Horada, źmiescavanaha na Stupienistych Kamianiach.
Žychary Volnaha Horada, źmiescavanaha na vyśpie ŭ Letnim Mory.
Ja ździŭleny, što vy nie paznali sumna viadomaha Zabojcy Karala. Ja ser Džejmi z Domu Łańnistaraŭ.
Ja ŭsadziŭ svoj mieč u śpinu karala, jakoha paklaŭsia baranić, tym zasłužyŭ hety tytuł.
Chacia ja klatvaparušnik i zabojca, nie havoručy pra maje inšyja złačynstvy, zabojstva Šalonaha Karala, vierahodna, było maim samym bieskarysnym učynkam. Bo jon spaliŭ by ŭsio karaleŭstva.
Ja nie hańbuju vas, my ŭsie majem minułaje.
The Lion of Lannister, oh how the mighty have fallen.
My father only cares about his legacy and my sister is screwing the whole kingsguard. Ive had enough the games they play in Kings Landing. From this day forth, Im just Jaime.
Oh, so you dont know who I am? I knew who you were. My little birds tell me everything.
I am none other than the Master of Whisperers my dear sir, nothing escapes my ears that happens in the realm.
Even a company of valiant heroes such as yourself and your comrades could use what I provide. It may just halt the arrow coming from the rear, or even from within.
Although I lack physical prowess, my skills are of a different sort.
But yet spiders do bite and their venom can take down even a beast of a man.
Even for my band of warriors, you may still prove useful.
Spin your web elsewhere, word games matter little with arrows flying at your head.
This better be good, or your chicken is mine. Sandor Clegane it is.
I a killer just like all the men you see here.
And dont pretend you dont enjoy it.
There nothing sweeter than seeing a prick gasp for his last breath of air.
A fellow with your size and attitude that is still alive must be a beast on the battlefield.
What the hell is your problem?
I will slice a man from nave to chop and not loose a wink of sleep. Just dont get in my way when I find my dear brother.
Only if you have a full coin purse.
I sell my sword, really my only talent other than sticking my nose two inches deep in that one over there.
The names Bronn, although now I am an annointed knight, I may still be your man if the price is right.
So if you dont mind, Im about to go smell the roses.
I feel you, who do you recommend?
Come on man, I thought you wanted to talk business.
Hire me, job done, no questions asked, except one, how much?
Hello sir, dont mind me, just passing through on my way to Castle Black.
I was once the heir of House Tarly, but my father banished me and deemed me unworthy.
Perhaps hes right, maybe I deserve it. I was never the valiant warrior he wanted me to be.
Im just a pudgy, coward of a man, with my nose stuck in books instead of what a true lordly youth should do.
Dont be so hard on yourself. A father like that is no father at all.
In this grim land, cowards are easy prey.
Can I follow your caravan? You wont even know Im there.Ive learned a few things about stymying infection from all the books Ive read.
Dont judge be by my house. My cousin, the Kings Justice scares me too.
Im not much of a warrior yet, but I did slay a Kingsguard on the battlefield.
I can cook, clean and help you with your armor.
You want regret having me around. Ill make sure of that.
Just a smiths apprentice from Flea Bottom.
The names Gendry. Dont know if Im a Hill, Rivers or Storm, but a bastard without a doubt.
Every warband needs someone to knock out dents and sharpen swords if my smiths hammer is more of use to ya.
Anybody would want to get out this shit hole and say whatever to do it.
No doubt you would pulverize something.
I got the strength and endurance of an ox from pounding steel from dawn til dusk.
I havent ever touched a battlefield, but put a war hammer in my hands and see what happens.
Why the googly eyes? You never saw a dwarve before.
I saved all of Kings Landing at the Battle of the Blackwater and what thanks did I get, a demotion and a hole where my nose used to be.
I drink and know more than ever these days. Slurp!.
I do need some new armor, can you shit me out a few golden dragons.
What need do I have for an imp to guzzle all my ale.
You seem to be a clever guy, youll figure it out.Now if you would excuse me.
My father is Selwyn if Evenfall Hall.
Honor, duty and loyalty are of upmost importance of knighthood.
Although Im not a knight, I live by this creed regardless.
What a beast of a woman you are!
People like you are hard to find, I applaud you.
If you will have me, my sword is yours till my dying breathe.
For your purposes, you may call me Jaquin Hagar.
A mans path was not random, this encounter guided by the Many-faced god.
In service to the Many-faced god.
To be be unseen but yet seen a man must do.
Mysterious, I need to here more.
I once led travelers to and from the Eyrie.
Through the highest and most trecherous mountains in all of Westeros with nothing but my donkey.
A girl with good pathfinding skills should be helpful.
I could be your scout or perhaps lead a caravan. I would love see the world with you.
This world will swallow a country girl like you alive.
Im trained in the arts of medicine.
But lost my chains for exploring my medical curiosity in a, shall I say, unorthodox way.
My skills still remain though. The ability to cure diseases, prolong life and of course, other things you may find useful.
Keep my soldiers from dying and you are a friend of mine.
I shudder to think of atrocities you must have committed.
Keeping your men alive and untapping their complete potential, by whatever means necessary, is my utmost goal, dear sir.
I was once the First Sword of Bravos.
From where Im from, true swordsmanship is an art form. Not just hacking away as you do here.
A duel is not a test of wills but a water dance.
I need swords, no matter if the one you use is pencil thin.
There is no where to dance when youre surrounded or backed into a corner.
The First Sword of Bravos faced worse odds and yet he lives.
Damn, you got to have giants blood.
You dare approach a Dothraki Blood rider!
What do you want ifak? Unless your paying for my time, I wont be interested.
My name is Rago, I was a Bloodrider for a Khal from the east. Protected his back, gave him counsel, even shared his Khaleesi. Life was grand.

After some time, my Khal thought he was much stonger than he was. The chiftik thought he could challenge the great Khal Drogo. Suffice to say, Drogos hair has never been cut. I had warned my Khal many times he could not win. He refused to listen. Afterwards I brought his Khaleesi to Vaes Dothrak.
Then what are you doing here sulking and drinking?
Atleast you gave him that honor.
Now I travel the world, so that one day I may avenge my fallen Khal and go to the night lands with honor.
I was once one of the richest men in Qarth.
The mother of dragons refused my advice, destroyed our citys great trading economy
I left a blood stained glove on her pillow and now sail for home.
Are you mad!? You started a war with the mother of dragons?
The richest man in Quarth, perhaps your future is still bright.
Let me ask do you think the path from poverty to wealth is always pure and honorable? No? Then you and I could forge our own path together.
I am Kinvara, a priestess of the lord of light
Everyone is what they are and where they are for a reason. Terrible things happen for a reason.
Daenerys Stormborn is the one who was promised. From the fire she was reborn to remake the world... She has freed the slaves from their chains and crucified the Masters for their sins...
Her dragons are fire made flesh, a gift from the Lord of Light.... Daenerys has been sent to lead the people against the darkness in this war and in the great war still to come
Youre no different than any other priestess. Insane, and following a dream.
I have heard of the prestigous ways of the priests of light.
I will spread the word of the lord of light, no matter what you believe.
I am Osha of the Freefolk
I am a spearwife. A woman warrior from the beyond the wall.
After being freed from my bonds of slavery to the north. I have been searching for my place in the world
Winter is coming, and we must prepare all that we can.
Youre a wildling? We would never trust the likes of you.
Come Spearwife! Lets prepare them together!
True freedom, is only know to us wildlings.
I am Shagga of the Stone crows!
A stone crows axe is always sharp. Shaggas axes are sharpest of all!
Shagga once cut a mans head off so fast, he didnt even know til he went to brush his hair!
Shagga works for anyone for the right price.
Shagga is a monster, who should be put down
Ah! Shagga I have heard of your people, join me and we will spill lots of blood together!
Careful, or Shagga remove your manhood and feed it to the goats!
Let me ask you do You Know What Its Like To Be Told How Lucky You Are To Be Someones Prisoner?
I was a prisoner of the starks for a long time. After Eddards death, I left to make my own way.
Now I wish to prove myself worthy to stand on my own, without the Starks, without my father.
Youre nothing more than a common pirate, with even less honor.
Follow me into battle, and your name will be remembered.
My Sword Is Yours, In Victory And Defeat, From This Day Until My Last Day.
I have a great set of skills, from tending dogs, to warming your bed.
After my lover showed he was more interested in others, I split my own way.
My Father was a kennelmaster at the dreadfort. Mmm. Have you ever seen a body after the dogs have been at it? Not so pretty.
I cant imagine having you by my side.
Come, even if you dont warm my bed, there is plenty of others in my party who need that.
*She chuckles* This is going to be so much fun!
After my fathers crucification in Mareen, I set out to find allies to help restore the city to its past glory
What is done is done. I am a servant of Meereen; a servant who does not wish to see its traditions eradicated.
Perhaps you would help restore my great city?
Slavery is not something I would support in my vision of the world.
Maybe you could help guide my hand to learn the customs of Mareen?
Then let us build it together.
All those lords and ladies, still think that the only thing that matters is gold.
You can imagine Jaimes Lannisters amazement when I chopped off his hand.
That his gold couldnt save him. His noble name couldnt save him.
I am one of the best hunters of the north. I have served the Boltons, and for the right reason I may serve you.
I have no use for a cut throat like yourself.
You and I could see the rise of a new empire, where all the nobles of westeros must bend the knee to common men.
Sounds like a dream I would sign up for.
I served Stannis Baratheon for many years, advising in science and medicine.
He turned away from the light of the seven. Listening to the guidance of a red witch.
Now I look to find myself in a new station, where my advice is wanted.
What use do I have for an old man?
Medicine and Science, who couldnt use an advisor of your stature?
My Gratitude for appreciating my wisdom my lord.
I was knighted by the late Robert Baratheon for my valor at the siege of Pyke
Ive protected queens, kings, and all sorts of noble men.
Now, I sit here wasting, drinking this ale.
A knight shouldnt be wasting away in this crappy tavern. Can you still fight?
I would protect you at all costs, honor means all to a man of my stature.
I spent my younger days fostered by the Yronwoods to settle a blood debt.
I was once promised the throne of Dorne, fate changed the plans though. Now I must obtain glory.
The hero sets out with his friends and companions, faces dangers, comes home triumphant. Only some of his companions dont return at all. The hero never dies, though. I must be the hero
This hero has no need for a Martell.
Come join us then, there will be plenty of glory to be had.
This will be my grand adventure!
Chaos isnt a pit. Chaos is a ladder. Many who try to climb it fail, and never get to try again.
The fall breaks them. And some are given a chance to climb, but refuse. They cling to the realm, or the gods, or love... illusions.
Only the ladder is real. The climb is all there is
Climb your way back to the gutter and leave me be.
Perhaps we will climb that ladder together Little Finger? Riches and nobility all lie in my destiny.
Then we shall climb to the sun.
I am Yoren a wandering crow.
one day, Willem came riding back into town. And I buried an axe so deep into Willems skull they had to bury him with it. Willems horse got me to the Wall and Ive been wearing black ever since.
I am on a quest to recruit more men to the nights watch.
Maybe you wish to bring honor to your name? Take the black?
What in the gods makes you think I would take the black?
Join my cause, and I will make it my mission to provide you with fresh men to defend the wall.
As long as I can try to acquire more men to defend the wall, and a belly full of food. Ill protect your back.
A word? I know lots of words. Tell me which your highness wants to hear, and Nimble Dick will say it..
I like to see a king dance, hey-nonny hey-nonny hey-nonny ho..You ever hear of Ser Clarence Crabb?

Ser Clarence Crabb, I said. I got his blood in me. He was eight feet tall and so strong he could uproot pine trees and chuck them half a mile. No horse could bear his weight so he rode an aurochs. His wife was a woods witch.

Whenever Ser Clarence killed a man, hed fetch his head back home and his wife would kiss it on the lips and bring it back t life. Lords, they were, and wizards and famous knights and pirates. One was king o Duskendale. They gave old Crabb good counsel. Being they was just heads, they couldnt talk real loud, but they never shut up neither. When youre a head, talkings all you got to pass the day. So Crabbs keep got named the Whispers.
You know what! Youre the kind of Dick I could use in my party! Lets go!
Old Dicks a harmless fellow. Chivalrous as a knight, and honest as the day is long.
I usually fight for House Lannister
But I may have gambled my gold away.
I can pledge my sword to you for a price.
I could use someone like you in my ranks
How can I trust a Lannister.
A Lannister always pays their debts.

Majo imia Kryhan Biełakryž. Ja mieč na prodaž.
Za maleńkuju sumu maniet ja harantuju biaśpieku vam ci vašaj siamji, jak heta rabili maje prodki ŭ čas paŭstańniaŭ Skahosaŭ.
Pieršy ŭ historyi Biełakryž zahinuŭ, baroniačy maładoha šlachciča Minańnia Zimy.
Dziakuj za ŭrok historyi, pryjemna viedać, što vy majecie hłybokija karani, jakimi lha hanarycca.
Dobra, mnie prosta patrebien vašy ščyt na maim boku. Spadziajusia, vy hetak ža mocnyja na spravie, jak u hutarkie.
Tak, spadziajusia, maje prodki buduć mnoju hanarycca.
Mianie kličuć Bendžen Stark, ja prysiahnuŭsia Načnomu Dazoru.
Kali vy padarožničajecie za miežami ściany, vam spatrebicca pravadyr.
Vam paščaścić, kali vy sutyknieciesia tolki z ledzianymi pavukami, cienievymi katami i strašnymi vaŭkami.
Sardečna zaprašaju, zdajecca, vy padychodzicie dla pracy.
My rušym ŭ šlach z pieršymi pramieniami sonca.
